    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that defines showroom quality. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its deep, factory-original luster without a single swirl mark, door ding, or stone chip. The exterior paint depth is consistent across all panels, reflecting a mirror-like finish. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and completely free of bolster wear or creasing, still carrying that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity surround sound system to the panoramic navigation interface, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive, documented service history performed exclusively by brand-certified technicians. With exceptionally low mileage and a driving profile that feels as tight and responsive as the day it was delivered, this is a rare opportunity for a discerning enthusiast. The sale includes all original manuals, two master keys, and a pristine maintenance log detailing its pampered life.",
